{"tid":1603371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［對外掃盲］9.29大戰，全因警察未遊行先射催淚彈！","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T20:00:11.000Z","uid":87553,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a21d03c821095ce32ac0098ff0342c6a5cf6793c","tid":1603371,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"我知道今日打到七國咁亂，黑警用盡各種卑鄙手段襲擊市民，但外面嘅人、外傳未必咁清楚件事，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢哋只會話「今日又有暴力示威」</strong></span>。呢個係香港群眾於不義，令外國逐漸對香港人嘅請求卻步！<br />\n<br />\n以路透社為例，睇下佢哋點寫今日嘅事？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixPAtQU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixPAtQU.png&h=46af7210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://reut.rs/2mO3ISJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freut.rs%2F2mO3ISJ&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=0c930fd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reut.rs/2mO3ISJ</a><br />\n<br />\n問題係外人未必知咁多前因後果，加上去到最後雙方都有出手，冇跟實件事嘅人好難分清楚邊個啱同錯。結果傳媒就會寫到變成雙方大戰，甚至好似上面咁，寫到警察好似係正常處理示威咁，對於正當企出嚟嘅香港群眾大大不利。<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好灰心住！重有一件事可以清楚界定是非！<br />\n<br />\n就係今日喺遊行開始(下晝3點)之前，警察已經用催淚彈攻擊喺銅鑼灣嘅人。當時甚至未有大規模聚集！由於件事喺遊行之前發生，除咗党媒之外，都好難再扭曲成為「執法」、「因混亂而驅散」！<br />\n<br />\n我哋要一齊向出面嘅人、外國人講清楚發生咩事！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>不要說</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Polices fired tear gas at protestors （警察向示威者發射催淚煙：令人誤解警察係正常應對）<br />\nViolent clashes between polices and protestors （示威者與警察暴力衝突：將市民一方正當行為同警暴混為一談）</span><br />\n<br />\n試想說<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Polices attacked civilians with tear gas grenades before the march （警察於遊行前以催淚彈襲擊平民）<br />\nCitizens flocked onto streets after polices stormed the shopping district （警察襲擊購物區後，市民湧上街頭）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足要記得，打仗唔淨止係上場，事件解讀、話語權對爭取後續支持都好緊要，和理非、勇武同文宣係絕一不可。今日開始喺social media講多啲，幫手導正返外間嘅誤解，你同我都做得到！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d327122f13ce53201d6c68cdb55ec74bc39df0a2","tid":1603371,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷地留低負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b00680a47d74d40fb0568f01f56c221eaca664","tid":1603371,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc754e66bdf2672a146a1715b17142ec2a30650","tid":1603371,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:46:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港人治港 剷除共黨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">正名!</span></span><br />\n狗 --&gt; 港共走狗/共狗打手/金腰帶<br />\n示威者 --&gt; 香港人<br />\n死--&gt;被自殺<br />\n藍絲--&gt;港共流氓<br />\n<br />\n光頭警長劉Sir前往内地安家，民眾甚感期待<br />\n光頭<span style=\"color: red;\">走狗</span>劉Sir前往内地安家，民眾甚感期待<br />\n<br />\n[底已起] 又有隻奶共狗話示威者係曱甴<br />\n[底已起] 又有隻奶共狗話<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span>係曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權! 撐政府一律捆綁式形容!</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8b2f356c9aa8910568ca36eb064cc99476e1bd9","tid":1603371,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"LEAVE NAME"},{"pid":"c58b0992d486c85b60920436700451fdb14d0dcf","tid":1603371,"uid"